<section class="section s5-process">
  <div class="container">

    <h2 class="s5-process__heading">Simple, Professional, and Supportive</h2>

    <div class="s5-process__grid">

      <div class="s5-process__col">
        <h3 class="s5-process__col-title">Personalized Consultation</h3>
        <p class="s5-process__col-body">Your session begins with a brief consultation with one of our registered nurses. They will review your wellness goals and answer any questions to ensure your treatment is perfectly suited to your needs.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-process__col">
        <h3 class="s5-process__col-title">Relax and Recharge</h3>
        <p class="s5-process__col-body">Once settled in our comfortable therapy lounge, the IV drip is administered. The process is virtually painless and takes about 45-60 minutes. You can relax, read, or catch up on emails while your body absorbs the nutrients.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="s5-process__col">
        <h3 class="s5-process__col-title">Feel the Support</h3>
        <p class="s5-process__col-body">Many clients experience a sense of revitalization and well-being after their session. The goal of these therapies is to provide foundational support for your body's systems over time. Consistent treatments are designed to complement your overall health plan and help you feel your best.</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>
